channel.title: My list of issues
channel.description: Okay, so while they're not giant issues, they kinda inhibit my gameplay experience. I recently dl'd the Zenithscape ps, and it runs smoothly, except for when I watch in commands, sometimes it'll say missing packet 85 or 93. Is there a way I can fix this? I'm completely new to Java, so if I have to go in depth or something, could I get step by step instructions. Second, I can't access anything in- game. When I try to go to a bank, it says "nothing interesting happens" the same with all shops. Can someone help me?
